metadata.description:
FX_D3M0NS is a fun Generative PFP project designed to give back to the Tezos Community and most importantly spotlight some INCREDIBLE artist.  I have wanted to create a D3M0N collection that was Generative for a while, and I also have a DEEP PASSION for showcasing other artist which led me to a great idea.  This project has been a goal of mine for a long time and I am truly Excited because of the artists that got involved.  It will be fun to see a canvas from an artist as profile picture, thus making the "skin" of the D3M0Ns the artists spotlight.  Have fun collecting and please share your favorites!

